$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
add_sentence

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_sentence -  This method raises a player's sentence count in the specified area
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int add_sentence(string place_name,
mixed player)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^place_name%^RESET%^ - the name of the place to raise the count in
%^BOLD%^player%^RESET%^ - the name or object of the player to raise the count for
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if successfully added, 0 if not

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/crime_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method raises a player's sentence count in the specified area
.EP

